  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个HealthTech系统的数据流转图。核心是从EMR同步模块出发，处理患者记录的分发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，EMR_Sync作为起点。那患者记录节点是单一的还是需要多个？我看业务上可能涉及不同科室的数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要多个。从EMR_Sync先连到一个患者记录节点，然后这个节点要分出三条路径：两条到不同的患者记录分支，一条回到EMR_Sync做反馈。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了：A是EMR_Sync，指向B患者记录，B再分出C、D两个患者记录节点，以及E回到EMR_Sync。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。现在C这条线要回到EMR_Sync，然后I节点再从EMR_Sync出去。D那条线要连到诊断引擎。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "F",
        "I",
        "D",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "C指向F，F再连回EMR_Sync作为I？不对，F应该直接到I，I是EMR_Sync。D指向G诊断引擎。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "F",
        "I",
        "D",
        "G"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "F到I是对的，但I是EMR_Sync，F也是EMR_Sync？让我理一下：C患者记录处理后回到EMR_Sync，这个节点我们叫F，然后F再输出到I，I也是EMR_Sync？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "F",
        "I"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可能是两次同步操作？或者F是中间状态，I是最终同步。我先按C→F→I画，都是EMR_Sync类型。E那条线呢，B直接回到的E也是EMR_Sync。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "I"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，E是快速反馈回路，F-I是深度处理链路。现在E还要往下走到H，H是检验分析模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "H",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "E指向H检验分析。G诊断引擎也要往下走吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "H",
        "G"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "G诊断引擎输出到J，J回到EMR_Sync。H检验分析输出到K，K是患者记录节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "G",
        "J",
        "H",
        "K"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "G→J→EMR_Sync，H→K→患者记录。现在I和J都是EMR_Sync，它们后面怎么连？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "I",
        "J",
        "K"
